com.interpss.core.net
Interface Network

All Superinterfaces:
EMFPersistable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAdaptable, IMultiNet, INetBranchElement, INetBusElement, INetworkElement, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
AclfNetwork, AcscNetwork
All Known Implementing Classes:
AclfNetworkImpl, AcscNetworkImpl, NetworkImpl
public interface Network
extends NameTag, IAdaptable, INetworkElement, INetBusElement, INetBranchElement, IMultiNet, EMFPersistable

A representation of the model object 'work'. The base network container class for buses and branches.

The following features are supported:

  • Base Kva
  • Frequency
  • Contain Child Net
  • Bus Number Arranged
  • Zero ZBranch Processed
  • Data Checked
  • Bypass Data Check
  • Sensitivity Calculated
  • Allow Parallel Branch
  • Check Element Duplication
  • Allow Ground Branch
  • Switch Break Model
  • Original Data Format
  • Ref Bus Type
  • Ref Bus Id
  • Parent Net Interface Bus Id
  • Branch List
  • Bus List
  • Zone List
  • Area List
  • Tie Line List
  • Owner List

See Also:
NetPackage.getNetwork()
